s/charts/base` is run\\n24: - **THEN** no errors or warnings related to chart metadata are reported\\n25: \\n26: ---\\n27: \\n28: ### Requirement: values.yaml default key tree\\n29: \\n30: The chart SHALL provide a `values.yaml` with the full key tree documented in the deployment design, including typed defaults for `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis.addr`, `redis.password`, `router` (replicas, image, service, resources, config, extraEnv, serviceAccountName, rba...\n  Line 16: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775872122263,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c62e4dffe2yL2bTDMDrVotb\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3a190200106egdn38S7twcf\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a3a0698001DcRjcKjWm0cmdp\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285c62e4dffe2yL2bTDMDrVotb\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_514dfa5942b141acba9f23a7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Design/设计说明\\n2: \\n3: ## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\\n4: \\n5: ### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\\n6: \\n7: `manifests/charts/base` 是 AgentCube 控制面栈的 Helm Chart，提供参数化的 Kubernetes 资源模板，支持一键安装、升级和回滚。Chart 驱动 Workload Manager、Router、可选 Volcano 调度器的完整部署生命周期，通过 `values.yaml` 集中管理所有可配置参数（镜像、副本数、资源配额、Redis 连接、环境变量覆盖）。\\n8: \\n9: Chart 是 E2E 测试、生产部署、开发者本地 Kind 集群的统一入口，消除手动编辑 YAML 的需求。\\n10: \\n11: ### 1.2 包结构 (Package Layout)\\n12: \\n13: ```\\n14: manifests/charts/base/\\n15: ├── Chart.yaml                              # Chart 元数据 (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0)\\n16: ├── values.yaml                             # 默认配置值树 (Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano)\\n17: ├── crds/\\n18: │   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml    # AgentRuntime