chart SHALL provide a `values.yaml` with the full key tree documented in the deployment design, including typed defaults for `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis.addr`, `redis.password`, `router` (replicas, image, service, resources, config, extraEnv, serviceAccountName, rba...\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775871354095,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d44ddaffeDHwNq0O3Y6Wjb1\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a2e60a6001Iu9XkMIuaSj4XG\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a2e418c001BWPcRPumT5f6oF\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d44ddaffeDHwNq0O3Y6Wjb1\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_4bdb321eef7f47008ca49ef3\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Tasks\\n2: \\n3: > **Module:** manifests\\n4: > **Language:** YAML\\n5: > **Size:** L\\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-030/design.md`, `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\\n8: > **Dependency:** `make gen-crd` 已可用（或 CRD 手工编写）\\n9: \\n10: ---\\n11: \\n12: ## T-001: Chart.yaml 元数据\\n13: \\n14: - [ ] T-001.01 创建目录 `manifests/charts/base/`\\n15: - [ ] T-001.02 创建 `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml`\\n16: - [ ] T-001.03 设置 `apiVersion: v1`\\n17: - [ ] T-001.04 设置 `name: agentcube`\\n18: - [ ] T-001.05 设置 `description: A Helm chart for AgentCube`\\n19: - [ ] T-001.06 设置 `version: 0.1.0`\\n20: - [ ] T-001.07 设置 `appVersion: 1.0.0`\\n21: \\n22: **验收**: `python3 -c \\\"import yaml; d=yaml.safe_load(open('manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml')); assert d['apiVersion']=='v1' and d['name']=='agentcube' and d['version']=='0.1.0' and d['appVersion']=='1.0.0'\\\"` 无报错\\n23: \\n24: ---\\n25