 Workload Manager, Router, optional Volcano scheduler, RBAC resources, and CRDs into a single installable unit with configurable values.\\n15: \\n16: ### 1.2 Chart Structure\\n17: \\n18: ```\\n19: manifests/charts/base/\\n20: ├── Chart.yaml\\n21: ├── values.yaml\\n22: ├── crds/\\n23: │   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\\n24: │   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml\\n25: └── templates/\\n26:     ├── _helpers.tpl\\n27:     ├── workloadmanager.yaml\\n28:     ├── agentcube-router.yaml\\n29:     ├── rbac/\\n30:     │   ├── workloadmanager.yaml\\n31:     │   └── router.yaml\\n32:     └── volcano/\\n33:         └── agent-scheduler.yaml\\n34: ```\\n35: \\n36: ### 1.3 Components\\n37: \\n38: | Component | Kind | Required | Description |\\n39: |-----------|------|----------|-------------|\\n40: | Workload Manager | Deployment + Service | Yes | Agent session management |\\n41: | Router | Deployment + Service | Yes | API routing lay...\n  Line 19: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775871596545,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285ce6281ffekEVhHvlf3nPcA5\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a32121c001WSM5birr92AuFP\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a31ebce00178Z7FfDZxjBKTl\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285ce6281ffekEVhHvlf3nPcA5\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_abdbae64bdcb4f4188ad2612\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md\",\"limit\":100},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values\\n2: \\n3: ## Overview\\n4: \\n5: This delta-spec defines acceptance scenarios for implementing the Helm Chart templates and values configuration for deploying AgentCube to Kubernetes, providing a reusable, configurable deployment mechanism for the Workload Manager, Router, optional Volcano scheduler, and associated RBAC resources.\\n6: \\n7: ## Base Specifications\\n8: \\n9: - **AR**: AR-030\\n10: - **Module**: `manifests`\\n11: - **Language**: YAML\\n12: - **Size**: L\\n13: - **Base Specs**: `deployment/spec.md`, `deployment/design.md`\\n14: \\n15: ---\\n16: \\n17: ## Background\\n18: \\n19: AgentCube requires a standardized deployment mechanism to Kubernetes clusters. The deployment/spec.md document defines the expected chart structure, but the actual template files need implementation. The Helm chart enables reproducible deployments, configuration management via values.yaml, namespace-scoped installations, optional components (RBAC, Volcano scheduler), and CRD lifecycle management.\\n20: \\n21: ---\\n22: \\n23: ## Requirements\\n24: \\n25: ### AR-030-001: Chart 结构与元数据\\n26: \\n27: The Helm chart SHALL provide proper structure and metadata for Helm 3 compatibility.\\n28: \\n29: #### Scenario: AR-030-001-A — Chart.yaml 包含正确的元数据\\n30: \\n31: - **GIVEN** a chart directory at `manifests/char...\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775871628437,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285ce6281ffekEVhHvlf3nPcA5\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a3236a7001kq6BhtPSc3ndo4\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a322bbb001vXeis12lUzt2fo\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285ce6281ffekEVhHvlf3nPcA5\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_0c4ea956e9224889a6ab09d2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"error\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Task Checklist\\n\\n**AR ID**: AR-030  \\n**Module**: manifests  \\n**Language**: YAML  \\n**Size**: L  \\n**Stage**: ST-3 (Implementation)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Phase 1: Chart Structure & Metadata\\n\\n- [ ] T001: Create directory `manifests/charts/base/`\\n- [ ] T002: Create `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` with apiVersion=v2, name=agentcube, version=0.1.0, appVersion=1.0.0\\n- [ ] T003: Create `manifests/charts/base/values.yaml` with all documented keys (redis, workloadmanager, ro