\n15: ├── Chart.yaml                              # Chart 元数据 (apiVersion v1, name agentcube, version 0.1.0)\\n16: ├── values.yaml                             # 默认配置值树 (Redis, Router, WorkloadManager, Volcano)\\n17: ├── crds/\\n18: │   ├── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml    # AgentRuntime CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\\n19: │   └── runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml # CodeInterpreter CRD (v1alpha1, Namespaced)\\n20: └── templates/\\n21:     ├── workloadmanager.yaml                # WM Deployment + Service\\n22:     ├── agentcube-router.yaml               # Router Deployment + Service\\n23:     ├── rbac/\\n24:     │   └── workloadmanager.yaml            # WM ServiceAccount + ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding\\n25:     ├── rbac-router.yaml                    # 可选 Router ServiceAccount + Role + RoleBinding\\n26:     └── volcano-agent-scheduler-development.y...\n  Line 8: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775871003063,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a2903d3001lVz5revIaRo19g\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a28f59c001xaYdOcRgV6cI4S\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_55d13f64b5a04283b01af8e1\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030: Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Delta Spec\\n2: \\n3: ## Context\\n4: \\n5: - **Module:** `manifests`\\n6: - **Language:** YAML\\n7: - **Size:** L\\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/spec.md`, `deployment/design.md`\\n9: \\n10: ## Delta Requirements\\n11: \\n12: ### Requirement: Chart.yaml metadata\\n13: \\n14: The chart SHALL define `Chart.yaml` with `apiVersion: v1`, `name: agentcube`, `version: 0.1.0`, and `appVersion: 1.0.0`.\\n15: \\n16: #### Scenario: Chart metadata fields are correct\\n17: - **GIVEN** the file `manifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml` exists\\n18: - **WHEN** it is parsed as YAML\\n19: - **THEN** `apiVersion` equals `v1`, `name` equals `agentcube`, `version` equals `0.1.0`, and `appVersion` equals `1.0.0`\\n20: \\n21: #### Scenario: Helm lint passes on chart metadata\\n22: - **GIVEN** a valid `Chart.yaml` with the fields above\\n23: - **WHEN** `helm lint manifests/charts/base` is run\\n24: - **THEN** no errors or warnings related to chart metadata are reported\\n25: \\n26: ---\\n27: \\n28: ### Requirement: values.yaml default key tree\\n29: \\n30: The chart SHALL provide a `values.yaml` with the full key tree documented in the deployment design, including typed defaults for `imagePullSecrets`, `nameOverride`, `fullnameOverride`, `redis.addr`, `redis.password`, `router` (replicas, image, service, resources, config, extraEnv, serviceAccountName, rba...\n  Line 9: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775871004086,\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7a290a2b0015vuDeAB1eVt5nx\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7a28f59c001xaYdOcRgV6cI4S\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_285d94d8fffeNOnrGGHJVfF0qU\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_147138be58fa4c77be044d15\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-030/tasks.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-030 — Helm Chart 模板与 Values — Tasks\\n2: \\n3: > **Module:** manifests\\n4: > **Language:** YAML\\n5: > **Size:** L\\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-030/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-030/design.md`, `changes/AR-030/delta-spec.md`\\n8: > **Dependency