etadataService` 是 CLI 核心的元数据管理组件。当前实现存在以下问题:\\\\n12: 1. `AgentMetadata` 位于 `services` 包，而非 `models` 包\\\\n13: 2. 缺少 `update_metadata` 方法\\\\n14: 3. 缺少语言特定的工作区验证\\\\n15: 4. `MetadataOptions` 缺少 `from_options` 类方法\\\\n16: \\\\n17: ### Goal\\\\n18: \\\\n19: 1. 迁移 AgentMetadata 到 models 包统一管理\\\\n20: 2. 实现完整的 MetadataService CRUD 操作\\\\n21: 3. 添加语言特定验证逻辑\\\\n22: 4. 增强 MetadataOptions\\\\n23: \\\\n24: ### Value\\\\n25: \\\\n26: - **模块化**: 数据模型与业务逻辑分离\\\\n27: - **可维护性**: 统一的模型定义位置\\\\n28: - **完整性**: 完整的元数据生命周期支持\\\\n29: - **可验证性**: 语言特定工作区验证\\\\n30: \\\\n31: ---\\\\n32: \\\\n33: ## Scope\\\\n34: \\\\n35:...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-023_ST-7.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775864567259,\"sessionID\":\"ses_286393f55ffe5cb8pHqVc20fEy\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d79c6d25e0013Lkoc8iq4vAS4j\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d79c6c1840013Fv0WPUBLsJwvS\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_286393f55ffe5cb8pHqVc20fEy\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"toolu_153e19189b024c138870b7a7\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"path\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark\",\"pattern\":\"AR-023\"},\"output\":\"Found 134 matches (showing first 100)\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z_logs/AR-023_ST-6.log:\\n  Line 38: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":1775864559739,\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_2863a8e69ffehRilhpu9IffRAw\\\",\\\"part\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"prt_d79c6a4f9001asbS2ROMr1Qr3P\\\",\\\"messageID\\\":\\\"msg_d79c681b7001eHDZaAjEwq7z5a\\\",\\\"sessionID\\\":\\\"ses_2863a8e69ffehRilhpu9IffRAw\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"text\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"## Verification Results for AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令\\\\n\\\\n### Summary: ✅ SPEC COMPLIANT, 103/103 tests passing\\\\n\\\\n| Spec Requirement | Status |\\\\n|------------------|--------|\\\\n| **Package Layout** | ✅ All required modules exist |\\\\n| **Console Script** | ✅ `kubectl-age